metadata.name: Wisdom
metadata.description: Fran Rodríguez aka lacabezaenlasnubes (spanish for "head in the clouds") is a digital artist based in Tarragona, Spain. He is famously known for his striking images depicting his interpretation of humanity’s place in the universe. Fran’s work is deeply inspired by his early fondness of surrealism and psychedelia. In his 20 year career, he has worked with bands such as Weezer, Tame Impala and Twin Shadow creating visual elements for their concerts and albums.
